ygData.subject: Re: Lute of the Gypsy Princess
ygData.msgSnippet: At 30th level, The Lute of the Gypsy Princess I keep stored in the bank does nothing different than a standard lute. You can test this with the Hymn if you
ygData.messageBody:
At 30th level, The Lute of the Gypsy Princess I keep stored in the bank does
nothing different than a standard lute. You can test this with the Hymn if
you want. It may only effect certain other stringed songs, I do not know,
but Hymn was the easiest to test, I believe.

Tim - Tallonn
